Initialize phase:

Prepare notes for every learning action that you take below. It is invaluable, mandatory.

Learn HTML and CSS from MDN Docs, refer forth and back to new resources to understand better the concepts.
Learn Javascript and JAvascript DOM.
Revise complete React from official docs of React.
Build at-least 2 projects of your own.

Iterate phase: to become Mid level:
Master HTML and CSS, by searching for the tutorials that take our skill to the next level.
LEarn Twitter Bootstrap with React.(Optional)
Learn ReactJS again by taking any other course again. This will not only refresh your memory but also makes you adept at basic topics.

Interview Phase: to clear Interview:
REvise all notes prepared. Collect interview questions from all possible sites where JS is discussed.
Continue building your own projects to keep in touch with basic react coding.
